quran[9{c,v,t}:
6,19,"un se pucho, kis ki gawahi sab se barh kar hai? kaho, mere aur tumahray darmain Allah gawah hai, aur yeh quran meri taraf ba zarea wahi bheja gaya hai taakay tumhe aur jis jis ko yeh puhanche, sab ko mutnabba kar dun kya waqai tum log yeh shahadat day satke ho ke Allah ke sath dosray khuda bhi hain? kaho, mein to is ki shahadat hargiz nahi day sakta kaho, khuda to wohi aik hai aur mein is shirk se qatee bezaar hon jis mein tum mubtala ho"
6,20,jin logon ko hum ne kitaab di hai woh is baat ko is terhan ghair mushtaba tor par pehchante hain jaisay un ko apne beiton ke pehchanney mein koi ishtibaah paish nahi aata magar jinhon ne apne aap ko khud khasaray mein daal diya hai woh isay nahi mantay
6,21,"aur uss shakhs se barh kar zalim kon hoga jo Allah par jhoota bohtan lagaye, ya Allah ki nshanyon kojhutla-ay? yaqeenan aisay zalim kabhi Falah nahi pa satke"
6,22,jis roz hum un sab ko akhatta karen ge aur mushrikon se poucheen ge ke ab woh tumahray tehra-ay hue shareek kahan hain jin ko tum apna khuda samajte thay
6,23,to woh iss ke siwa koi fitnah nah utha saken ge ke ( yeh jhoota bayan den ke ) ae hamaray aaqa! teri qasam hum hargiz mushriknah thay
6,24,"dekho, uss waqt yeh kis terhan apne oopar aap jhoot gharein ge, aur wahan unn ke saaray banawati mabood gum ho jayen ge"
6,25,"un mein se baaz log aisay hain jo kaan laga kar tumhari baat suntay hain magar haal yeh hai ke hum ne unn ke dilon par parday daal rakhay hain jin ki wajah se woh is ko kuch nahi samajte aur un ke kaanon mein gharani daal di hai ( ke sab kuch suneney par bhi kuch nahi suntay ) woh khuwa koi nishani dekh len, is par imaan laa kar nah den ge hadd yeh hai ke jab woh tumahray paas aa kar tum se jhagarte hain to un mein se jin logon ne inkaar ka faisla kar liya hai woh ( saari baatein suneney ke baad ) yahi kehte hain ke yeh aik daastaa’n Parinah ke siwa kuch nahi"
6,26,woh is amar haq ko qubool karne se logon ko roktay hain aur khud bhi is se daur bhagtay hain ( woh samajte hain ke is harkat se woh tumhara kuch bigaar rahay hain ) halaank darasal woh khoo daal apni hi tabahi ka samaan kar rahay hain magar inhen is ka shaoor nahi hai
6,27,kash tum is waqt un ki haalat dekh satke jab woh dozakh ke kinare kharray kiye jayen ge is waqt woh kahin ge ke kash koi soorat aisi ho ke hum duniya mein phir wapas beje jayen aur apne rab ki nshanyon ko nahjjhutlain aur imaan laane walon mein shaamil hon
